    The diagonal blocks are identities.  Below the diagonal, the block in
    column `j` is the stage-`j` multiplier `AрхбР▒╝^(j) AР▒╝Р▒╝^(j)РЂ╗┬╣`, represented by
    the supplied `pivotInv j`.  Above the diagonal the factor is zero. -/
