  exact higham13_problem13_4_A21_rectOpNorm2Le_of_full_operator_bound
    A hRho_ge_one hA

/-- Higham, 2nd ed., Chapter 13, Problem 13.4:
    the upper-left inverse principal block inherits a rectangular operator-2
